---
import PublicLayout from '../../layouts/PublicLayout.astro';
---

<PublicLayout
  title="Products"
  description="Tools built by smagile to help professionals and teams work better. Mosaic CV: one career, infinite CVs."
>
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 sm:py-20">
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-grey-900 dark:text-white">Products</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-grey-700 dark:text-warm-200">
      Tools we build to solve real problems.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-12">
      <!-- Mosaic CV -->
      <a
        href="https://mosaic.smagile.co"
        class="group block p-8 sm:p-10 bg-secondary-50 dark:bg-grey-800 rounded-xl border border-secondary-200 dark:border-grey-700 hover:border-accent/40 dark:hover:border-secondary/40 transition-all hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-accent/5"
        rel="noopener"
      >
        <!-- Gold accent bar -->
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-6 right-6 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-accent-light/60 to-transparent"></div>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-start gap-6">
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-grey-900 dark:text-white font-heading">
              Mosaic CV
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-accent dark:text-accent-light font-medium">
              One career. Infinite CVs.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-4 text-grey-700 dark:text-warm-300 leading-relaxed">
              Your career is multifaceted. The same experience, pitched differently, unlocks
              completely different opportunities. Mosaic stores your experience once, then helps
              you tailor it for any role, any industry, any seniority level.
            </p>
            <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-grey-700 dark:text-warm-300">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-primary dark:text-secondary mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
                AI-powered gap analysis that guides, never fabricates
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-primary dark:text-secondary mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
                ATS-optimised output in PDF and Word
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-primary dark:text-secondary mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
                GDPR compliant with full data portability
              </li>
            </ul>
            <span class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-primary dark:text-secondary font-medium group-hover:gap-2.5 transition-all">
              Try Mosaic CV free
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
              </svg>
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-16 text-center px-4">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-grey-800 dark:text-white font-heading">
      Building something and need help?
    </h2>
    <div class="mt-4 mx-auto w-16 divider-gold"></div>
    <p class="mt-6 text-grey-700 dark:text-warm-300 max-w-xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
      We also help teams improve the way they work. If your team is struggling with delivery,
      we should talk.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-8">
      <a
        href="/how-we-help/"
        class="inline-block px-8 py-3.5 bg-primary hover:bg-primary-dark text-white font-medium rounded-lg transition-all shadow-lg shadow-primary/20 hover:shadow-primary/30 hover:-translate-y-0.5"
      >
        See how we help teams
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</PublicLayout>
